1081
01:16:03,329 --> 01:16:04,849
Shut up and come with me.

1082
01:16:06,769 --> 01:16:07,768
Get in.

1083
01:16:27,529 --> 01:16:30,089
Tell her the truth.
- I’ll tell you…

1084
