1106
01:17:42,529 --> 01:17:44,049
Sure. I will

1107
01:17:55,288 --> 01:17:56,248
Hey...

1108
01:17:56,929 --> 01:17:59,849
You proved that you are genuine in your love.

1109
01:18:00,009 --> 01:18:03,009
