die with you, Is all this cheating?

1296
01:32:27,544 --> 01:32:30,624
She cared for you more than your parents

1297
01:32:30,705 --> 01:32:31,944
If she really cared about me so much,

1298
01:32:32,104 --> 01:32:34,824
